com.tlswe.awsmock.ec2.servlet

Class MockEc2EndpointServlet

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • com.tlswe.awsmock.ec2.servlet.MockEc2EndpointServlet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    public class MockEc2EndpointServlet
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
    Servlet implementation for mock ec2 endpoint. This servlet works as an AWS ec2 endpoint that accepts AWS Query API request and respond bare xml, with aws-sdk, ec2-api-tools, elasticfox and other clients.
